The most beautiful swimming pools in Europe
Jump into the blue
By Julia Stanek
Planschpools with UFO optics, showpools in Budapest: If you travel through Europe, you can experience its blue wonder - and after a city tour or a hike, rest your tired legs in bubble baths.
