She has travelled through 13 countries on her "journey to the most extraordinary baths in Central Europe": in addition to Germany, Austria and Switzerland, she has visited places in Italy, France, the Czech Republic, Slovakia, Slovenia, Hungary, Romania, Poland - and one city each in Luxembourg, Serbia and Croatia.
The 46-year-old German is a true bath culture enthusiast.
She's not much for sports, Meder says - only in the water.
